<TextSection>
  <h3 id="born-to-run">1. "Born to Run" by Christopher McDougall</h3>
  <p>
    This memoir chronicles the author's journey to discover the secrets of the
    Tarahumara Indians, who are known for their incredible running skills. "Born
    to Run" is a must-read for anyone interested in the science behind human
    endurance.
  </p>
  <ProductsContainer products={1} />
</TextSection>
