<TextSection mxw="">
  <h3 id="mamba-mentality">2. "Mamba Mentality" by Kobe Bryant</h3>
  <p>
    In the wake of his retirement from professional basketball, Kobe “The Black
    Mamba” Bryant decided to share his vast knowledge and understanding of the
    game to take readers on an unprecedented journey to the core of the
    legendary “Mamba mentality.”
  </p>
  <ProductsContainer products={1} />
</TextSection>
