<TextSection mxw="">
  <h3 id="into-thin-air">3."Into Thin Air" by Jon Krakauer</h3>
  <p>
    This memoir delves into the devastating 1996 Mount Everest disaster, which
    claimed the lives of eight climbers. Krakauer offers an intimate and
    gripping account that will leave you on the edge of your seat.
  </p>
  <ProductsContainer products={1} />
</TextSection>
