  <h3 id="the-boys-in-the-boat">
    4. "The Boys in the Boat" by Daniel James Brown
  </h3>
  <p>
    This biography follows the journey of the University of Washington's rowing
    team as they prepare for the 1936 Olympics in Nazi Germany. Brown's book is
    a powerful and poignant tale of perseverance and determination.
  </p>
  <ProductsContainer products={1} />
</TextSection>
<!-- </li> -->
