<TextSection mxw="">
  <h3 id="endurance-a">5. "Endurance" by Alfred Lansing</h3>
  <p>
    This biography follows the journey of explorer Ernest Shackleton and his
    crew as they attempt to cross Antarctica in 1914. Lansing's meticulous
    research and vivid writing make for an exhilarating and gripping read.
  </p>
  <ProductsContainer products={1} />
</TextSection>
<!-- </li> -->
