  <h3 id="a-walk-in-the-woods">6. "A Walk in the Woods" by Bill Bryson</h3>
  <p>
    This memoir follows Bryson's attempt to hike the Appalachian Trail with his
    friend Stephen Katz. Bryson's humor and wit make for a truly entertaining
    and engaging read.
  </p>
  <ProductsContainer products={1} />
</TextSection>
