  <h3 id="the-river-of-doubt">9. "The River of Doubt" by Candice Millard</h3>
  <p>
    This biography follows Theodore Roosevelt's incredible journey down the
    uncharted River of Doubt in the heart of the Amazon. Millard's writing is
    thrilling and suspenseful, offering a vivid portrait of one of America's
    most beloved presidents.
  </p>
  <ProductsContainer products={1} />
</TextSection>
